            <div class="section-component">
				<div class="step-icon"><span>1</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">1.</span> 登录 Azure 官网 www.azure.cn，点击页面右上角的“我要购买”，就可以开始申请了。</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-signup-and-new-step_01.jpg" id="azure-1rmb-trial-and-signup-and-new-step_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-signup-and-new-step_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
					<p>请点击<span><a href="/pricing/pia/" target="_blank">我要购买</a></span></p>
