				<div class="step-icon"><span>2</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">2.</span> 进入 <span>Azure 预付费产品购买申请表页面</span>，根据需要选择“个人申请”或“企业申请”。</h2>
					<table width="100%">
						<tr style="background-color:#4f81bd">
							<td style="color:#fff">若您选择的是 “个人申请”：</td>
							<td style="color:#fff">若您选择的是 “企业申请”：</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td width="50%">
								<dl>
									<dd>1) 输入手机号码后，进行手机验证即可进入下一步。</dd>
									<dd><a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_1_01.jpg" id="pia-new02_1_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_1_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
									</dd>
								</dl>
							</td>
							<td><dl>
								<dd>1) 输入手机号码后，进行手机验证即可进入下一步。</dd>
								<dd><a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_2_01.jpg" id="pia-new02_2_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_2_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
								</dd>
							</dl>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>
								<dl>
									<dd>2) 填写申请人姓名、身份证字号、邮箱，并上传您的身份证正反面照片后，点击“提交”。您将立即获得实名认证的审核结果，若审核通过，您将自动进入注册页面。</dd>
									<dd><a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_1_02.jpg" id="pia-new02_1_02" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_1_02.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
									</dd>
								</dl>
							</td>
							<td>
								<dl>
									<dd>2) 填写申请人姓名、邮箱、企业全称、统一信用代码，并上传企业营业执照图片后，点击“提交”。您将立即获得企业实名认证的审核结果，若审核通过，您将自动进入注册页面。</dd>
									<dd><a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_2_02.jpg" id="pia-new02_2_02" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new02_2_02.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></dd>
