				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>3</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">3.</span> 账户注册</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_03.png" id="azure-wire-transfer-pia-new-step_03" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_03.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>4</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">4.</span> 登录账户</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_04.png" id="azure-wire-transfer-pia-new-step_04" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_04.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>5</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">5.</span> 进入<span>付款页面</span>，你可以选择“电汇“方式进行付款。</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_05.jpg" id="azure-wire-transfer-pia-new-step_05" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_05.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>6</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">6.</span> 显示汇款说明</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_06.png" id="azure-wire-transfer-pia-new-step_06" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_06.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>7</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">7.</span> 进行电汇</h2><br/>
					<p><strong>汇款信息如下</strong></p>
					<table>
						<tr>
							<th></th>
							<th><b>中文</b></th>
							<th><b>ENGLISH</b></th>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>开户银行/Bank</td>
							<td>汇丰银行（中国）有限公司北京分行</td>
							<td>HSBC Bank (China) Company Limited, Beijing Branch</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>账户名称/Account Name</td>
							<td>上海蓝云网络科技有限公司</td>
							<td>Shanghai Blue Cloud Technology Co., Ltd</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>银行账号/Bank Account</td>
							<td colspan="2" align="center">626-144927-011</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>银行国际代码/Swift Code</td>
							<td colspan="2" align="center">HSBCCNSHBJG</td>
						</tr>
					</table>
					<p><strong>备注</strong></p>
					<p>请在转账汇款时备注您的订阅 ID，以便于我们区分汇款来源。</p>
					<p>您可登录<a href="//account.windowsazure.cn/subscriptions" id="pricing-billing-transfer_subscriptions" target="_blank">订阅管理门户</a>, 点击订阅名称，页面右侧会显示“订阅 ID“。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>8</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">8.</span> 提交汇款资讯</h2><br/>
					<p>订单提交后两个工作日，您将收到“订单通知”的提醒邮件，请根据内容提示回复该邮件；</p>
					<p>或者您也可直接填写以下汇款信息发送到 azure_invoice@oe.21vianet.com，以便我们区分汇款来源并及时充值到您的订阅账户。</p>
					
						<p>1. 订阅 ID（登录<a href="//account.windowsazure.cn/subscriptions" id="pricing-billing-transfer_subscriptions2" target="_blank">https://account.windowsazure.cn/subscriptions</a>, 点击订阅名称，页面右侧会显示“订阅 ID” ）</p>
						<p>2. 汇款金额:</p>
						<p>3. 汇款日期:</p>
						<p>4. 汇款银行账号</p>
						<p>5. 汇款人姓名（汇款底单上的汇款人）:</p>
						<p>6. 公司名称:</p>
						<p>7. 联系人手机:</p>
					
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>9</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs">9</span> &nbsp;充值成功</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_09.jpg" id="azure-wire-transfer-pia-new-step_09" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-new_09.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
					<p>友情提示：在汇款到账与以上汇款信息匹配成功后，我们会在两个工作日内将汇款金额充值到您的订阅账户。</p>
					<p>同时您会收到“购买确认”的通知邮件，也可在您的订阅账户下看到充值的金额。</p>
				</div>
